        "text_673jrG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Anyone can perform a scan. Knowing what the data reveals — and what it does not — is where professional competence begins.<br/><br/>Bio-Well education programmes are built on a simple premise: measurement without interpretation is noise. Our structured curriculum moves practitioners from raw output to contextual analysis, grounded in three decades of GDV research and over 400 peer-reviewed publications. This is not a product tutorial. It is a scientific education programme designed to develop genuine analytical capability.<br/><br/></p><ul><li><strong>Interpret electrophotonic data with precision and context</strong></li><li><strong>Understand variables, protocols, and the limits of measurement</strong></li><li><strong>Develop structured professional reports that stand up to scrutiny</strong></li><li><strong>Align your practice with published scientific methodology</strong><br/><br/><br/></li></ul>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
