        "text_UMj7FR": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>In-Depth Training for Professional Mastery</h3><p>The Advanced Bio-Well Certification Program is designed for practitioners, therapists, researchers, and health professionals who want to develop a comprehensive understanding of electro-photonic measurement, structured interpretation, and real-world application.</p><p>This program transforms Bio-Well users into confident, certified professionals capable of delivering structured analysis and meaningful insights within their field of practice.</p><h3>What You Will Learn</h3><p>Through this advanced certification course, participants develop the ability to:<br/></p><ul><li>Interpret electro-photonic measurements beyond raw numerical outputs</li><li>Understand variability, context, and influencing factors affecting Bio-Well data</li><li>Identify meaningful patterns and trends across sessions</li><li>Build clear, structured professional reports</li><li>Apply Bio-Well technology responsibly within therapeutic, wellness, or research environments</li><li>Integrate measurement insights into broader professional frameworks</li></ul><p>The course combines scientific foundations, applied methodology, and advanced interpretation techniques. Participants learn how to move beyond raw data, understand patterns and variability, and integrate Bio-Well measurements into structured professional workflows.</p><p>Delivered online, the program offers flexible learning while maintaining a high level of academic and practical rigor. It forms the core of Bio-Well education and leads to professional certification supported by expert instruction and structured modules.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-lg",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
            "text_capitalize": false,
            "secondary_color": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
