        "text_CyT7Gj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Dmitry Orlov</strong><em><br/>Founder of Bio-Well · Physicist · Researcher</em></h3><p>Bio-Well education programmes are developed and directed by Dmitry Orlov — physicist, researcher, and the principal scientific mind behind the Bio-Well technology.</p><p>With decades of research in electro-photonic emission, gas discharge visualization (GDV), and ultra-weak biological signals, Dmitry Orlov has played a central role in transforming experimental science into a structured, applicable system for professional use.</p><p><br/>His work bridges fundamental physics, biological research, and real-world clinical application — forming the scientific foundation upon which every Bio-Well certification programme is built.</p><p>Hundreds of scientific publications. 65 countries. Thousands of trained professionals. One methodology. </p>",
